headline: All You Need to Know About Northern Trust (NTRS) Rating Upgrade to Strong Buy
summary: Northern Trust (NTRS) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #1 (Strong Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.

headline: Northern Trust Names Jesse Crane Pacific Northwest Regional Director for Foundation & Institutional Advisors
summary: SEATTLE, December 04, 2024--Northern Trust announced today that Jesse Crane has joined the Foundation & Institutional Advisors (FIA) practice as Regional Director for the Pacific Northwest. Based in Seattle, Crane will provide investment solutions to the firm’s foundation, endowment and institutional nonprofit clients.
